data.description: ''ASSUMABLE VA LOAN AT 3.5% IF QUALIFIED''   Cute and Bright home with 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms.  There are 2 bedrooms that are attached to bathrooms making them both masters. Great for a mother-in-law or teenager.  New flooring was just professionally installed in the living and hall areas.  The wood burning fireplace is a great touch to get cozy on these cold nights.  Ceilings are 12 foot height and this is an open floorplan with split bedrooms.  The backyard has a privacy fence with a picket along the backside because there are no rear neighbors.  Just a few blocks to the white sandy beaches.  This home is clean and comes complete with Refrigerator, Washer and Dryer that are only 3 yrs old.  The HVAC was replaced 3 yrs ago too and is maintained with a maintenance contract.  Come see this great starter home or possible Airbnb in a perfect location. Flood insurance is transferable.
